#: ../../wallets/android/advanced-functions.rst:110
msgid ""
"The Dash Android Wallet is a light wallet and functions in SPV mode, meaning"
" it does not download a full copy of the blockchain. The network monitor "
"allows you to view details about the full nodes to which you are connected. "
"You can also swipe left to view blocks as they are created on the "
"blockchain."
msgstr ""

